high_descs: Turn left and go to the counter between the fridge and the stove.
Pick up the lettuce that is on the counter.
Look downwards while holding the lettuce.
Put the lettuce back down on the counter.
Pick up the knife that is next to the potato.
Use the knife to slice the lettuce.
Put the knife back down on the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn left and go to the refrigerator.
Put the lettuce on the middle shelf of the refrigerator for a few seconds, then take it back out.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the lettuce in the right side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled slice of lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Go straight and to the left to the counter on the left side of the oven.
Take the lettuce from the counter.
Stay at the counter.
Put the lettuce on the upper right hand corner of the counter.
Take the knife from the counter.
Cut the lettuce into slices on the counter.
Put the knife on the counter on the potato.
Take a slice of lettuce from the counter.
Go left to the refrigerator next to the counter.
Put the lettuce on the middle shelf of the refrigerator. Close then open the refrigerator. Take the lettuce from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Walk forwards and then turn right towards the counter next to the stove
Take the lettuce from the counter
Walk back with the lettuce
Put the lettuce on the counter again
Take the knife from the counter
Slice the lettuce on the counter
Put the knife on the counter again
Take a slice of the lettuce
Walk with the slice of lettuce and towards the fridge and open it
Put the slice of lettuce inside the fridge, close it and open it again
Take the slice of lettuce from the fridge and walk towards the sink
Put the slice of lettuce inside the sink
anns.task_desc: Slice the lettuce, take a slice put it on the fridge then on the sink
